# Tory, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Tory (; , Toor) is a rural locality (a selo) in Tunkinsky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population was 876 as of 2010. There are 18 streets.
Geography
Tory is located 67&nbsp;km east of Kyren (the district's administrative centre) by road. Dalakhay is the nearest rural locality.
